# ArchMock MVP Scope

**IN scope**:
- Auth (email + Google OAuth via Clerk)
- 10 curated SD problems
- Whiteboard with custom SD shapes (service, DB, cache, queue, LB, CDN, client, storage, zone, arrow)
- DiagramGraph extraction from canvas
- Chat with AI interviewer (Claude Sonnet, streaming)
- Real-time diagram observation (graph JSON only — no vision/PNG)
- Interjection engine — AI reacts to canvas changes
- Final evaluation (Claude Opus)
- Session history with results
- PDF export of session

**OUT of scope** (Phase 2+):
- Voice agent
- Vision-based diagram analysis / PNG snapshots
- Billing / Stripe
- Multiplayer
- Community problems
- Marketplace / B2B dashboard

When implementing, do not add Phase 2+ features. Stick to the MVP checklist in the implementation plan.
